  "subject": "Fix: Remove unused sphinx-toolbox dependency",
  "commit_message": "Fix: Remove unused sphinx-toolbox dependency\n\nRemove sphinx_toolbox.collapse from conf.py extensions and sphinx-toolbox\nfrom requirements-docs.txt. The extension is unused in this repository\n(no collapse directives in RST content) and sphinx-toolbox 4.1.2 is\nincompatible with Sphinx 9.x, breaking RTD builds.\n\nSee the doc repository for full details and migration guidance.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Iafbdd54583e1a88dd42d1bc42bca100080bb8792\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
